main event: A civilian reported seeing a luminous object in the sky that appeared to be hovering and changing in intensity over Cyprus Gardens, Florida in August 1961.
interesting points: The object made a very bright light and was several times brighter than the largest star.
The object seemed to be hovering about 30 degrees above the horizon.
The witness watched the object for about 10 minutes before it faded away.
The object changed in intensity a few times while the witness was watching it.
The witness was unsure if they should report the sighting to anyone.
